// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0325 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 4b23d4d7-829d-5407-ae19-9f059146174c

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:2*" or process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:2023*" or process.executable like~ "*azure linux:3.0*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*")
